                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260216-132-off698 t18260216-132-cd699"></join>, 1 watch, value 20s.; 1 watch chain, value 6d.; 2 seals, value 6d., and 1 watch key, value 3d., the goods of 
